186 performed by a network provider participating in the insured’s health benefit plan. Evidence that
187 an insured had a reasonable opportunity to choose to have the service performed by a
188 participating provider may include, but is not limited to, a consent waiver signed by the insured.
189 (g) The commissioner shall promulgate regulations to implement this section.
